      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what beauty? how can there be beauty when everything is just grey? i look at my apartment and i just see his things, and i feel like i'm just waiting for a pain that never actually lets up. it feels like a cycle that just never ends. it's exhausting to even exist like this.",
