    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont want to wait for cracks to appear. i dont want to wait months or years for things to maybe feel slightly better. it just feels like i'm being forced to endure this agony for no reason. if the pain is just going to keep coming back, why do i even have to keep going through it?",
